  "type": "PrimaryTheme",
  "number": 5716,
  "title": "middle age",
  "comment": "The period between youth and old age. Middle age is marked by physical strength and experience and should bring maturity and stability. Many of God's servants began ministry in middle age, often after having been prepared in their youth. Middle age may also bring complacency and the temptation to leave the devotion and commitments of youth.",
